# CustomProxy (Cleaned)
# Source: whxhuiq-creator/proxy-rules-clean (manual + blackmatrix7 ProxyLite + ACL4SSR ProxyLite)
# Cleanup actions:
#   - Removed 8 DOMAIN entries covered by DOMAIN-SUFFIX
#   - Removed 41 DOMAIN-SUFFIX entries covered by parent SUFFIX
#   - Removed 261 entries covered by DOMAIN-KEYWORD
#   - Replaced 6 stale Telegram CIDRs with 14 from official cidr.txt
#   - Removed 14 stale AWS/IBM SoftLayer ranges (legacy WhatsApp/Telegram)
#   - Removed 16 scattered legacy single-IP entries
#   - Removed 8 tail IBM/duplicate-Telegram entries
#   - Removed 19 CN-domestic legacy Google mirror IPs (China Mobile/Telecom/Beijing Gu Xiang)
# Note: 7 ccTLD SUFFIX rules (eu/hk/jp/kr/sg/tw/uk) preserved per user decision
# Note: 108.177.8.0/21 (Google) removed; covered by Google.list's 108.177.0.0/17
# Original: 1699 lines -> Cleaned: 1344 lines
#
# NAME: CustomProxy
# FORMAT: Surge rule-set
# SOURCES: old manual CustomProxy; blackmatrix7 ProxyLite; ACL4SSR ProxyLite

